        <item>
            <title>CaptiMac v2.3-beta.3</title>
            <pubDate>Fri, 11 Jul 2026 16:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>2303</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h3>🆕 What's New</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Apple Tips Onboarding</strong> — 9 interactive tips guide you through CaptiMac in 2 phases</li>
                    <li><strong>Developer ID Distribution</strong> — works on any Mac, notarized by Apple</li>
                    <li><strong>Multi-Provider Transcription</strong> — Groq + OpenAI + ElevenLabs in onboarding &amp; settings</li>
                    <li><strong>Emoji Toggle Tip</strong> — now part of the guided tour</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>🔧 Improvements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Ollama download with real-time progress + cancel</li>
                    <li>Coverage audit: 97% accuracy for all languages (Unicode-aware)</li>
                    <li>WhisperKit language code fix (Danish, German, etc.)</li>
                    <li>Provider switch isolation — no more stale URLs</li>
                    <li>LicenseManager warning fixed</li>
                </ul>
                <h3>🐛 Bug Fixes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>CapCut MP3 export now works (Joint Stereo + uppercase .MP3)</li>
                    <li>Fase 2 tips overlay animation fixed</li>
                    <li>Onboarding tips appear after onboarding, not during</li>
                    <li>Release notes synced to current version</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
